OL,3,CExecutive has agreed #55m in new
OL,4,Cfunding allocations
OL,6,FThe biggest allocation of #18.3
OL,7,Fmillion is going to the Department of
OL,8,FHealth, followed by #16.8million for
OL,9,Fthe Department for Infrastructure as
OL,10,Fwell as funding for the Department of
OL,11,FEducation and the Department for
OL,12,FCommunications.
OL,14,FFinance Minister John O'Dowd said the
OL,15,FExecutive is fulfilling its commitment
OL,16,Fto meeting public sector pay awards.
