OL,3,CExecutive has agreed #55m in new
OL,4,Cfunding allocations
OL,6,F"At December monitoring, I committed
OL,7,Fthat if any further funding became
OL,8,Favailable, I would move quickly to
OL,9,Fallocate this towards public sector
OL,10,Fpay pressures," he said.
OL,12,F"As an Executive we remain fully
OL,13,Fcommitted to supporting public sector
OL,14,Fpay.
OL,16,F"We have therefore agreed to allocate
OL,17,F#25million in additional resource
OL,18,Ffunding towards meeting health service
OL,19,Fand teacher pay costs."
