OL,3,CExecutive has agreed #55m in new
OL,4,Cfunding allocations
OL,6,F"While additional funding is welcome,
OL,7,Fit is nowhere on the scale required to
OL,8,Fmeet the challenges facing
OL,9,Fdepartments. Our public finances
OL,10,Fremain extremely constrained this year
OL,11,Fand going into next year," Mr O'Dowd
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"I remain committed to working in
OL,15,Fpartnership with my ministerial
OL,16,Fcolleagues to find a way forward on
OL,17,Fthe multi-year budget."
OL,19,FInfrastructure Minister Liz Kimmins
OL,20,Fwelcomed the additional capital
OL,21,Fallocation for her department.
