OL,12,Fplanning of critical infrastructure,
OL,13,Fadditional investment such as this is
OL,14,Falways helpful, especially as it will
OL,15,Fnow allow for targeted road
OL,16,Fmaintenance to be rolled out in the
OL,17,Fcoming weeks," she said.
